-- Buffett’s General Re Hires AIG’s Yu for Risk Management Post
-- B y   S u s a n n a   P a k
-- 2012-10-09T14:29:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-09/buffett-s-general-re-hires-aig-s-yu-for-risk-management-post.html
General Re-New England Asset
Management Inc., a unit of  Warren Buffett ’s Berkshire Hathaway
Inc., hired Mark Yu of  American International Group Inc. (AIG)  to
oversee enterprise risk for life insurers.  Yu will report to Jim Bachman, vice president of capital
management, Farmington, Connecticut-based GR-NEAM said today in
a statement distributed by Business Wire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
